    "title": "Front Office Manager - Lemon Tree Hotels Consulting Pvt Ltd - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "Grow your career with Lemon Tree Hotels Consulting Pvt Ltd! We are hiring a Front Office Manager for our Jabalpur team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Lemon Tree Hotels Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nLemon Tree Hotels Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Coordinate housekeeping and maintenance for room readiness\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Lemon Tree Hotels Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
